{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1961, "height": 2666, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [149, 696, 223, 1372], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二四九", "block_bbox": [167, 1990, 216, 2109], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜家阁", "block_bbox": [897, 228, 1182, 293], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜家闵，原名下庄沟，位于渑池县果园乡十公里处仰韶大杏产地。原属洛宁县（古名永宁县），后改属渑池县。其地原隶西村乡李家村，二十世纪八十年代初农村实行联产承包责任制后独立建制，杜家门下辖杜家阙、王家阙、酒馆院三个自然村，杜家阙为杜家阙村委会所在地。2005年并入果园乡。杜家阙村共有150余户、520余口人。杜家阙村杜氏始族为渑池坻坞西村杜氏九世。其世系为：", "block_bbox": [313, 404, 1769, 718], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公——名失传——名失传——名失传——名失传——名失传——世登——国敬——朝进。\n", "block_bbox": [318, 737, 1768, 850], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "清朝定鼎之后，朝进由永邑之下营村（今洛宁县河底镇营里村）迁居于下庄沟。其排行，下营碑列朝宦为行三，杜家阙云和神轴列朝进为行三、朝宰为行四。碑为嘉庆五年（1800）立，轴为同治九年（1870）制，排行应以碑为确信。而云和神轴中朝宰，显为朝宦之误。因此，议拟杜家阙始祖朝进改行四。\n", "block_bbox": [316, 869, 1768, 1113], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9156963229179382, "coordinate": [313.591796875, 404.6668701171875, 1769.53466796875, 718.5406494140625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.897441565990448, "coordinate": [316.73876953125, 869.6236572265625, 1768.7314453125, 1113.6339111328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8573753833770752, "coordinate": [318.36712646484375, 737.770141601562