行四。碑为嘉庆五年（1800）立，轴为同治九年（1870）制，排行应以碑为确信。而云和神轴中朝宰，显为朝宦之误。因此，议拟杜家阙始祖朝进改行四。\n\n", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//3d0199d5-cbe7-4d42-b4ea-47b1c3856e91/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A19%3A10Z%2F-1%2F%2Ff7de3fd7643709dda68ee210a68a178b1583dfef163ecd72e89c4d903696cafa", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//3d0199d5-cbe7-4d42-b4ea-47b1c3856e91/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A19%3A11Z%2F-1%2F%2Fd20b40ca944f4384cd6ce22ca86da4046c682f9a1368f9e7aa178ee0056dae76", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//3d0199d5-cbe7-4d42-b4ea-47b1c3856e91/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A19%3A11Z%2F-1%2F%2F44a314870f1fd8d1f23cc85b840a9b8e2038ba9a7390fb15334f0c9795c67301", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//3d0199d5-cbe7-4d42-b4ea-47b1c3856e91/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A19%3A11Z%2F-1%2F%2F7453770290f09b0fa7f13701125aced4ada9c8792f42f8814e624616db557cb5"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//3d0199d5-cbe7-4d42-b4ea-47b1c3856e91/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A19%3A10Z%2F-1%2F%2F69a9eacbc5371b85a8dd20dff6e673af6989cd268dfb63d88aa6eb0c9ece07b5"}], "dataInfo": {"width": 1961, "height": 2666, "type": "image"}, "ocrResults": [{"prunedResult": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[899, 226], [1185, 226], [1185, 300], [899, 300]], [[446, 410]